"Project-Id-Version: libmessageviewer\n"
"Report-Msgid-Bugs-To: https://bugs.kde.org\n"
"POT-Creation-Date: 2026-02-09 10:14+0100\n"
"PO-Revision-Date: 2012-01-28 16:35-0800\n"
